description: I have a 24' Harris "Flote Bote" for sale. This is the 24 foot Cruiser model, very spacious and in very good condition. The lights work, the horn works, the radio did work in the summer, but seems to have a short that I can't find. I think its something simple because it will work now and then. I'm asking $7800.00 not because I "need" to sell it, but because I thought I would see if I could. It's a very nice boat that has been professionally maintained at a local marina.
